# TestEngine ‚Äî project context

## Stack

- **C++20**, single **`TestEngine`** target (CMake `WIN32` on Windows ‚Äî entry via `WinMain`; see `main.cpp`).
- **Build:** CMake 3.28+; build directory is usually **`build`** (not inside source roots). Details: [`BUILD.md`](BUILD.md).
- **Dependencies:** SFML, Dear ImGui + **ImGui-SFML**, **fmt** (`third-party/`). Python 3 is required at **configure** time (codegen).

## `src/` layout

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| **`Engine/App/`** | Entry (`main.cpp`), `EngineInterface`, input, fonts |
| **`Engine/Core/`** | Scene, nodes (`SceneNode`), properties/reflection (`MetaClass`, `IPropertiesProvider`, property trees) |
| **`Engine/Behaviour/`** | Base `Behaviour` ‚Üí components on nodes; subfolders by domain (e.g. `Physics/`) |
| **`Engine/Visual/`** | Rendering (shapes, text, arrows, etc.) |
| **`Engine/Editor/`** | ImGui editor widgets (hierarchy, inspector, property tree) |
| **`Engine/Simulation/`** | Simulation glue (e.g. physics ‚Äî `PhysicsHandler`) |
| **`Environments/<Name>/`** | Demos/games (**`Test`**, **`Pong`**); active environment is chosen in `main.cpp` (`TestEnvironment` / `PongEnvironment`) |
| **`Codegen/`** | Generated `*_gen.hpp` for the editor ‚Äî **do not edit by hand**; see [`property-codegen.mdc`](property-codegen.mdc) |

Sources are collected with **`file(GLOB_RECURSE ... src/**/*.cpp)`** ‚Äî after adding a **new** `.cpp`, run **CMake configure** again.

## Includes

Include roots: **`src/`** and **`src/Codegen/`**. Quote paths relative to those roots, for example:

```cpp
#include "Engine/Core/SceneNode.h"
#include "Environments/Pong/PongEnvironment.h"
```

## Code idioms

- **`Scene` / `SceneNode`**: entity hierarchy; nodes carry **`Behaviour`**s and visuals.
- **`EntityOnNode`**: binds an entity to a node; common base for behaviours.
- Editor and inspector rely on **`IPropertiesProvider`** and generated property trees ‚Äî read the **property-codegen** rule before adding reflected fields.

